  "rule_text": "The 'FLIP THE SCRIPT' display lockup sets the word 'THE' flipped upside down; 'ON IBS-C' is set in Avenir Light at 50% opacity, with the hyphen replaced by the brand swoosh at 100% opacity (see \u00a72.6). Uses asset ast_ibsrela_flip_the_script_lockup with the swoosh device ast_ibsrela_brand_swoosh.",
